Interface RemoteExecutionClients

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface RemoteExecutionClients
extends Closeable
    A Remote Execution service consists of two primary things, an execution service and a CAS. To use the service, we also need to ability to encode and decode various of the structures and this is provided by the Protocol.
